Bluetooth: blueman-applet

Dolphin theming:
- icons are here: /usr/share/icons/candy-icons/
    - had to delete 'master' from folder name and owned by my user
    - then i set this in ~/.config/kdeglobals:
    [Icons]
    Theme=candy-icons
- theme:
    - themes need to be installed in ~/.config/Kvantum/catppuccin-mocha-blue
    - theme has to have a .kvconfig file
    - after starting kvantummanager theme needs to be selected in the "change/delete" section

SDDM theming
- theme folder needs to be copied to /ust/share/sddm/themes
- to try a theme, do `sddm-greeter --test-mode --theme /ust/share/sddm/themes/sugar-candy`
    - to exit out of it do ctrl-c
- to set a theme, it needs to be set in /etc/sddm.conf as:
    [Theme]
    Current=tokyo-night-sddm





